'''Igor Sirtsov''' ([[Russian language|Rus]]: Игорь Сырцов) is a [[Kazakhs|Kazakhstani]] [[television producer]] and [[radio DJ]] who rose to popularity as a jury member in ''[[SuperStar KZ|SuperStar KZ 3]]'', the Kazakh version of ''[[Pop Idol]]''.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nv.kz/2005/10/26/7604/|title=«Мы не злые» Как понравиться жюри телепроекта "SuperStar.kz" ("We're not evil" How to appeal to the jury the TV project "SuperStar.kz")|last=Fomina|first=Natalia|date=26 October 2005|language=Russian|accessdate=11 January 2011}}</ref>

== Biography ==

Igor is the General producer of Kazakh television network [[KTK (Kazakhstan)|KTK]] and has been working in television since he was 16 years old. His career has also spanned radio in which he was the first commercial Kazakh radio DJ ever in the country.

